title: Miss Fury Digital #1 - 4 [Dynamite] (2013)
description:
Miss Fury Digital #1 - 4 [Dynamite] (2013)

When a time travelling Nazi secret agent wants to steal a Foo Fighter from the US military, who does he hire? A squadron of Roman Centurions of course. Its up to Miss Fury to stop a UFO falling into the hands of evil, and her battle will very quickly go from a rainy New York to the bomber filled skies over war ravaged Europe. Hang on for your life!!

**This is a separate series from the Miss Fury ongoing**
